name: NIKE Air Force 1 '07
description: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 is a men's lifestyle sneaker that will meet all your needs while celebrating the legacy of the AF1.They were designed as basketball sneakers, but in the nineties they find their place in hip-hop culture and become iconic sneakers around the world. To date, they have undergone over two thousand variations and have become a symbol of street fashion whose influence on culture, music and lifestyle cannot be denied. Strong seams, durable upper and rubber sole make them long-lasting and durable. Retro branding and colors provide a distinctive look.

name: NIKE Air Max 95 Essentia
description: Their iconic design draws inspiration from Japanese bullet trains, while refreshed colors and sharp details keep their look modern and fresh. Full-length Nike Air cushioning lets you move in first-class comfort. Mesh and synthetic materials on the upper maintain a fluid look, adding comfort and durability. Originally designed to provide good running performance, the full-length Nike Air unit perfectly unites maximum comfort and sporty style. The foam midsole is elastic and light. The rubber sole provides excellent grip and durability to these sneakers.

name: NIKE Dunk
description: Nike Dunk Low children's lifestyle sneakers are an indispensable part of your style. This basketball icon from the mid-80s returns with an extremely durable construction and original colors. Genuine and synthetic leather uppers are durable and deliver a classic feel. The full-length rubber outsole provides durable traction and features a pattern similar to the original. With ankle padding and a grippy rubber sole, this is a nail-biter.

name: NIKE GAMMA FORCE
description: Only a few styles have survived in sneaker history, and the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX sneaker is one of them. Celebrate perfection with what you know best: sharp leather on tops, bold details and the perfect amount of sparkle to shine. A stitched leather layer on the upper gives it a sporty heritage look, durability and support. Originally designed for basketball, Nike Air cushions provide lightness and all-day comfort. The reinforced heel is soft and comfortable, the Nike logo clearly speaks of your love for the brand.
